The '''[[Sith/Legends|Sith]] Assault Gun''' was a modification to the standard [[Blaster carbine/Legends|blaster carbine]] and was intended to be standard issue for [[Sith trooper (Sith Empire)|Sith troopers]]. It was rarely seen outside of Sith-controlled space and used extensively by [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] and [[Darth Malak|Malak's]] [[Darth Revan's Sith Empire|Sith Empire]] during the [[Jedi Civil War]].

